Sentencas: NiO-Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2 (YSZ) tubular type cell using La0.9Sr0.1Ga0.8Mg0.2O3- delta electrolyte film was prepared by dip-coating method.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: Effects of Ce infiltration or Ce, Ni sequential-infiltration into NiO-YSZ substrate were studied and it was found that Ce infiltration after Ni is highly effective for increasing the cell performance and the stability in fuel cell and electrolysis mode at 873 K in spite of decrease in performance by simple Ni infiltration.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: Cyclic operation of the fuel cell and electrolysis of LSGM tubular cell using Ce or Ce-Ni sequential-infiltrated NiO-YSZ substrate was measured at 873 K using 17% steam-25%H2 in Ar as fuel.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: After 100 cycles at +/- 0.1 A cm(-2), OCV was almost the same with the initial value.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: The terminal potential in SOFC operation became slightly lower with increasing cycle number in case of simple Ce infiltration.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: The main reason for degradation during cyclic performance seems to be assigned to the increased fuel electrode overpotential.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film

Sentencas: However, degradation rate is much decreased by Ce-Ni sequential-infiltration.
Titulo: Sequential-infiltration of Ce and Ni in NiO-YSZ fuel electrode for tubular type solid oxide reversible cells (SORC) using LaGaO3 electrolyte film
